        <div class="news-story">
          <h2><a href="{site_url}latest-news/rural-development-changes-interim-construction-financing">Rural Development Changes Interim Construction Financing</a></h2>
          <span class="date"> By Doug L. Baldessari, {if "CPA" != ""}CPA,{/if} {if "Partner" != ""}Partner,{/if} September 10, 2014<br />
          Latest News </span>
          <p>USDA Rural Development provides financing for water and wastewater infrastructure projects for rural areas in Indiana and across the country.  The program provides significant grant funding and also loan funding with up to a 40-year payback period.  The loan interest rates currently range from 2.375% to 4%.</p>
          <p class="readmore"><a href="rural-development-changes-interim-construction-financing">Read More &raquo;</a></p>
